headline: Northwest Natural (NWN) Q1 Earnings and Revenues Surpass Estimates
summary: Northwest Natural (NWN) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 9.09% and 3.37%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
